title: Rx SMS
about:
Back-end medication interaction app for text messaging. Users sign-up with their phone number and any medications they take. Once registered, they text a drug name to see if it interacts with their saved medications.

Includes: Node, MongoDB, Express, external API's, Mocha, Chai, and Gulp.

title: Bitmap Transformer
about:
Non-palette bitmap image transformer using simple command line arguments. Transformations include grayscale, a red hue, a mirrored image, all black, or inverted colors. This is an NPM installable package.

Includes: Node, Mocha, Chai, and Gulp

Source Code

title: Project Inoculation
about:
Web application allows users to search for K-12 schools in Washington state and discover vaccine exemption and completion rates. Utilizes Google maps and Chart.js to visualize data.

Includes: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery, Ajax, Page.js, Chart.js, Heroku, Firebase, MVC structure, mobile-first design

title: Welcome to Seattle
about:
This project provides users with a questionnaire to calculate the best Seattle neighborhood for their needs. Results include more detailed neighborhood information, Google maps, and an option to take notes.

Includes: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and Local Storage
